### Calculator API Testing
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5117

### Test Addition
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/add?a=10&b=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Subtraction
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/subtract?a=10&b=3
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Multiplication
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/multiply?a=4&b=7
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Division
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/divide?a=15&b=3
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Division by Zero (should return error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/divide?a=10&b=0
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Complex Calculation (Addition)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstOperand": 25.5,
  "secondOperand": 14.3,
  "operation": "+"
}

###

### Test Complex Calculation (Multiplication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstOperand": 8.5,
  "secondOperand": 2.5,
  "operation": "*"
}

###

### Test Complex Calculation (Division)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstOperand": 100,
  "secondOperand": 4,
  "operation": "/"
}

###

### Get Calculation History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/history
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Limited History (last 10 records)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/history?limit=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Clear History
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/calculator/history
Accept: application/json

